snippet.title: Super Monza GP 2 - VIC 20 (32K exp)
snippet.description:
Final lap around the Monaco circuit in my new game.  This builds upon the original game and now requires 32K expanded memory.  New features include 3 additional circuits, car damage and pitstops.

It can be downloaded here: https://aj-layden.itch.io/super-monza-gp-2
